<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Conta Aprovada - {{appName}}</title>
    <style>
        /* Base Styles */
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333333;
            background-color: #f9fafb;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        
        .email-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 30px auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 12px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
            border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        }
        
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #10b981 0%, #059669 100%);
            padding: 40px 20px;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
        }
        
        .brand {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        
        .brand-logo {
            width: 32px;
            height: 32px;
            background-color: #585ad4;
            border-radius: 8px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin-right: 12px;
        }
        
        .brand-name {
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: white;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        }
        
        .hidden-sm {
            display: none;
        }

        @media (min-width: 640px) {
            .hidden-sm {
                display: inline;
            }
        }
        
        h1 {
            color: #ffffff;
            font-size: 26px;
            margin: 10px 0 0;
            font-weight: 600;
            letter-spacing: -0.5px;
        }
        
        .content {
            padding: 40px;
        }
        
        h2 {
            color: #111827;
            font-size: 22px;
            margin-top: 0;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }
        
        p {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #4b5563;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        
        .highlight-box {
            background-color: #f0fdf4;
            border-left: 4px solid #10b981;
            padding: 16px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-radius: 0 6px 6px 0;
        }
        
        .button-container {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 35px 0;
        }
        
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 16px 32px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #10b981 0%, #059669 100%);
            color: #ffffff !important;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 16px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.3);
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
        }
        
        .button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.4);
        }
        
        .divider {
            height: 1px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(229,231,235,0) 0%, rgba(209,213,219,1) 50%, rgba(229,231,235,0) 100%);
            margin: 35px 0;
        }
        
        .footer {
            padding: 25px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #6b7280;
            background-color: #f9fafb;
            border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        }
        
        .social-links {
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        
        .social-icon {
            display: inline-block;
            margin: 0 8px;
            width: 36px;
            height: 36px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background-color: #e5e7eb;
            color: #4b5563;
            line-height: 36px;
            text-align: center;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        .social-icon:hover {
            background-color: #d1d5db;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }
        
        .footer-links {
            margin: 15px 0;
        }
        
        .footer-link {
            color: #6b7280;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin: 0 10px;
            transition: color 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        .footer-link:hover {
            color: #10b981;
        }
        
        @media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {
            .content {
                padding: 25px;
            }
            
            h1 {
                font-size: 22px;
            }
            
            h2 {
                font-size: 20px;
            }
            
            .button {
                padding: 14px 28px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="brand">
                <div class="brand-logo">
                    <svg 
                        xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" 
                        width="20" 
                        height="20" 
                        viewBox="0 0 20 20" 
                        fill="currentColor"
                        style="color: white;"
                    >
                        <path d="M10.394 2.08a1 1 0 00-.788 0l-7 3a1 1 0 000 1.84L5.25 8.051a.999.999 0 01.356-.257l4-1.714a1 1 0 11.788 1.838L7.667 9.088l1.94.831a1 1 0 00.787 0l7-3a1 1 0 000-1.838l-7-3zM3.31 9.397L5 10.12v4.102a8.969 8.969 0 00-1.05-.174 1 1 0 01-.89-.89 11.115 11.115 0 01.25-3.762zM9.3 16.573A9.026 9.026 0 007 14.935v-3.957l1.818.78a3 3 0 002.364 0l5.508-2.361a11.026 11.026 0 01.25 3.762 1 1 0 01-.89.89 8.968 8.968 0 00-5.35 2.524 1 1 0 01-1.4 0zM6 18a1 1 0 001-1v-2.065a8.935 8.935 0 00-2-.712V17a1 1 0 001 1z" />
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <span class="brand-name hidden-sm">{{appName}}</span>
            </div>
            <h1>Conta Aprovada!</h1>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <h2>Olá {{username}},</h2>
            
            <p>É com grande satisfação que informamos que sua conta na plataforma <strong>{{appName}}</strong> foi aprovada!</p>
            
            <div class="highlight-box">
                <p>Sua conta foi revisada e aprovada por <strong>{{reviewer}}</strong>. Agora você tem acesso completo a todos os recursos da nossa plataforma de ensino.</p>
            </div>
            
            <p>Você já pode fazer login e começar a explorar todos os materiais, cursos e ferramentas disponíveis para você.</p>
            
            <div class="button-container">
                <a href="{{loginUrl}}" class="button">Acessar Minha Conta</a>
            </div>
            
            <p>Se precisar de ajuda para começar, confira nosso <a href="{{helpUrl}}" style="color: #10b981;">guia de primeiros passos</a> ou entre em contato com nosso suporte.</p>
            
            <div class="divider"></div>
            
            <p><strong>Dúvidas ou problemas?</strong><br>
            Caso encontre qualquer dificuldade ao acessar sua conta, não hesite em nos contatar através do e-mail <a href="mailto:{{supportEmail}}" style="color: #10b981;">{{supportEmail}}</a>.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <div class="social-links">
                <a href="https://facebook.com/profile.php?id=61565792531619" class="social-icon">f</a>
                <a href="https://www.instagram.com/nordinomaviedev/" class="social-icon">ig</a>
                <a href="https://github.com/Mavton23" class="social-icon">git</a>
                <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/nordino-mavie-developer-ab6824357/" class="social-icon">lk</a>
            </div>
            <div class="footer-links">
                <a href="{{helpUrl}}" class="footer-link">Ajuda</a>
                <a href="{{terms}}" class="footer-link">Termos</a>
                <a href="{{privacy}}" class="footer-link">Privacidade</a>
            </div>
            <p>Atenciosamente,<br><strong>Equipe {{appName}}</strong></p>
            <p>© {{currentYear}} {{appName}}. Todos os direitos reservados.</p>
            <p><a href="mailto:{{supportEmail}}" style="color: #10b981; text-decoration: none;">{{supportEmail}}</a></p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>